Sandya's adhesive algorithms

(A)
Goal: Identifying poor Three Layer patterns
for c in PresentationPackage or Input
    if c.containsTooMuchLogic
        return false

 for c in DomainPackage
    if c.containsInput or Output
        return false
 for c in DataPackage
    if c.containsLogic or Output
        return false

