(C)
Goal: Identifying misspelled words

for class in package
    methods = class.methods()
    variables = class.variables()
    for m in methods
        for word in m
            if !dict.contains(word)
                return false
    for v in variables
        for word in v
            if !dict.contains(word)
                return false


(4)
Goal: Identify instances of missing implementations of abstract methods

for class in package
    methods = class.methods()
    for m in methods
        if m.HasException
            if m.catch < 2 lines
                return false

